{
  "texts": [
    "NV has created the modules of MANCHA for realistic simulations of solar and stellar convection, contributed to overall code's development and parallelization; he wrote Sections 2.3 -2.5.",
    "AdV introduced the actual code's modular structure and parallelization, performed multiple optimizations, and contributed to writing Section 4.",
    "AN programmed the heat conduction module and contributed to Section 2.1.",
    "PAGM programmed the STS and HDS schemes and contributed to Sections 3.1.2 -3.1.3.",
    "MCV co-authored the creation of the MANCHA code, contributed to its posterior development and simulation setups, and contributed to improving the paper text."
  ]
}